<a href="./MayLith">MayLith</a>: This page describes the abilities which you can view and/or buy by typing shift+n. These abilities may well be renamed as talents in the future, but in the meantime, I'm referring to them as "bought" abilities. <hr>
 <ol>
<li>
<a href="#head-2e70e399a4dd69eac0bab15f073cd5551832dae7">"Bought" abilities</a></li>
